high_descs: walk to the countertop in the kitchen.
pick up the cutting board with the bowl on top of the cutting board.
walk to the fridge and open the fridge door.
Put the bowl with the cutting board in the fridge, open the door and get the item out.
walk to the sink in the kitchen.
Put down the cutting board with the bowl on top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: moving the cutting board from Sink to Bowl.

high_descs: Walk straight to enter the kitchen and reach the countertop on the left.
Pick up the cutting board with the bowl from the counter.
Turn left to reach the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to reach the sink.
Put the cutting board on the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled cutting board with the bowl on the left sink.

high_descs: Go straight ahead into the kitchen area and turn to the counters next to the fridge.
Pick up the cutting board nearest the fridge that has a bowl on top of it.
Place the board and bowl into the fridge, let it cool, then retrieve it.
Place the board and bowl on the sink drainboard.
anns.task_desc: Put a refrigerated cutting board and bowl on a sink drainboard.
